=== AWESOMEBANNER ====================================================

Like SVR4 'banner' but more awesome!  Initially written for Solaris
but I cleaned it up to work on Linux as well.

--- Build ------------------------------------------------------------

  Solaris:
    cc  -lcurses  -o awesomebanner awesomebanner.c

  Linux:
    gcc -lncurses -o awesomebanner awesomebanner.c

--- Usage ------------------------------------------------------------

  ./awesomebanner 'Some Message'

----------------------------------------------------------------------
